3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper uses deep learning techniques to improve skin lesion classification, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with image classification of skin lesions, which is a multimedia application. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper uses specialized loss functions for the two related tasks, which is a technique used in information retrieval.
